<font size="2">( <a href="article.php?sid=140&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">comments?</a> | <a href="print.php?sid=140"><img src="images/print.gif" border=0 Alt="Printer Friendly Page" width="15" height="11"></a>&nbsp; <a href="friend.php?op=FriendSend&amp;sid=140"><img src="images/friend.gif" border=0 Alt="Send this Story to a Friend" width="15" height="11"></a> )</font>
