<font size="3" color="#FF7D00"><b>Deeper in the Halls of Honor...</b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="5" width="100%"><tr><td>
<font color="#FFFFFF"><b><a href="search.php?query=&amp;topic=13"><img src="images/topics/pix.gif" border="0" Alt="News" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10"></a></B></font><br>
<font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/ryddadar.JPG></center><br><br>We came, we saw...<br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/ryddardarcorpse.JPG></center><br><br>...we beat the shit out of it.<br><br>Halls of Honor is truly a great zone. The exp there is great, Spectral spell drops, nice loot from normal mobs and best of all, we can have ooc/shout turned on without being confronted with the stupidity that infects other zones.<br><br>It's also a nice looking zone, kinda reminds me of ancient Rome i guess. Nice and relaxing place, that is, when Rtyui isnt there.<br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/rtyuitrain.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/rtyuitrain2.JPG><br><br><br>As you can see from the top picture, we've been doing the trials in there too. Some have gone good, some have gone bad. Some have been, um, nothing less than catastrophus, but all in all it's good fun. Here's some pictures from other trials in there...<br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/crazed.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/trolls.JPG><br><br><br><b>Quotes of the day</b><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/ghazaki.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/hratli.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/hoh/hratli2.GIF><br><br><br>Stay tuned...</font>
</td></tr></table></table>
